Grammar

Rule 0     S' -> program
Rule 1     program -> statements END_PROG
Rule 2     statements -> statements statement
Rule 3     statements -> statement
Rule 4     statement -> ID IS expression
Rule 5     statement -> ID ARE expression
Rule 6     statement -> MAKE ID expression
Rule 7     statement -> PRINT expression
Rule 8     statement -> IF expression COLON statements EXCLAIM
Rule 9     statement -> IF expression COLON statements EXCLAIM ELSE COLON statements EXCLAIM
Rule 10    statement -> IF expression COLON statements EXCLAIM ELSE_IF expression COLON statements EXCLAIM
Rule 11    statement -> IF expression COLON statements EXCLAIM ELSE_IF expression COLON statements EXCLAIM ELSE COLON statements EXCLAIM
Rule 12    statement -> AS_LONG_AS expression COLON statements EXCLAIM
Rule 13    expression -> expression PLUS expression
Rule 14    expression -> expression MINUS expression
Rule 15    expression -> expression TIMES expression
Rule 16    expression -> expression OVER expression
Rule 17    expression -> expression LT expression
Rule 18    expression -> expression GT expression
Rule 19    expression -> expression IS expression QUESTION
Rule 20    expression -> expression ARE expression QUESTION
Rule 21    expression -> expression AND expression
Rule 22    expression -> expression OR expression
Rule 23    expression -> NOT expression
Rule 24    expression -> NUMBER
Rule 25    expression -> ID
Rule 26    expression -> STRING
Rule 27    expression -> TRUE
Rule 28    expression -> FALSE

